    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯两年内通过福克斯、书籍和演讲赚取了 600 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/hegseth-reaped-6-million-in-two-years-from-fox-books-speeches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择的五角大楼负责人皮特·赫格塞斯的财务披露声明，他过去两年的收入超过 600 万美元，包括担任福克斯新闻主持人的收入、书籍版税和演讲费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/hegseth-reaped-6-million-in-two-years-from-fox-books-speeches</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在外交政策告别会上表示，他将让美国变得更加强大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/biden-s-says-he-s-leaving-us-stronger-in-foreign-policy-farewell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在下周离任前发表演讲，吹捧自己的外交政策成就，并称他过去四年的行动为当选总统唐纳德·特朗普带来了更有利的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/biden-s-says-he-s-leaving-us-stronger-in-foreign-policy-farewell</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:04:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登高级助手沙利文称特朗普可能会保留新的人工智能芯片控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-likely-to-maintain-new-ai-chip-controls-top-biden-aide-jake-sullivan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府的一位高级官员表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普很可能会维持美国对英伟达公司等公司在全球销售人工智能芯片的新限制，理由是两党对中国追求先进技术存在国家安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/trump-likely-to-maintain-new-ai-chip-controls-top-biden-aide-jake-sullivan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将启动弹劾审判，决定尹永哲的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/south-korea-to-begin-impeachment-trial-to-decide-on-yoon-s-fate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国将于周二开始审判，以决定总统尹锡烈是否因其令人震惊的戒严令而被永久免职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/south-korea-to-begin-impeachment-trial-to-decide-on-yoon-s-fate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孤立的马杜罗如何继续在委内瑞拉掌权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/venezuela-where-things-stand-as-maduro-starts-contested-new-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管有证据表明委内瑞拉长期执政者尼古拉斯·马杜罗在 7 月份的总统选举中获胜，但他已宣誓就职第三个六年任期，此举引发了进一步的抗议、全球的广泛谴责和新的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/venezuela-where-things-stand-as-maduro-starts-contested-new-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 19:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部阿德耶莫前往哥伦比亚重点讨论能源制裁问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/treasury-s-adeyemo-heads-to-columbia-with-energy-sanctions-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，财政部二号人物沃利·阿德耶莫 (Wally Adeyemo) 将离开拜登政府，前往哥伦比亚大学任职，专注于经济治国和能源政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/treasury-s-adeyemo-heads-to-columbia-with-energy-sanctions-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:58:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省在关税迫在眉睫的情况下向特朗普推销矿业交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ontario-pitches-trump-on-mining-deals-with-tariffs-looming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对加拿大北方国家征收高额关税之际，加拿大人口最大省份的领导人正提议与美国在关键矿产方面建立“新的战略联盟”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/ontario-pitches-trump-on-mining-deals-with-tariffs-looming</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:34:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚财政部长称左翼领导人不能吓跑投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/finance-chief-seeks-to-soothe-colombia-investors-over-debt-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚新​​任财政部长迭戈·格瓦拉表示，哥伦比亚政府致力于保持公共债务的可持续性并保持投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/finance-chief-seeks-to-soothe-colombia-investors-over-debt-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省省长警告称，特朗普的关税即将到来，将包括石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯在佛罗里达会见美国当选总统后警告称，一旦唐纳德·特朗普下周就任总统，加拿大人应该准备好面对美国关税，石油产品将不会受到豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
